          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Maybe that was the reason for some of the crashes, but there are plenty of idiots who wreck out in high-powered, rear-wheel-drive cars with an independent rear suspension. Case in point: this C7 ",
