          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " driving next to an S550 Mustang on a four-lane road in Grafton, Illinois. Suddenly things take a turn for the worse, pun fully intended.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/10/Motorious--25.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "image credit: YouTube"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "You can hear the Z06’s LT4 supercharged 6.2-liter V8 rev. Then tire smoke kicks up as the American sports car lays down some rubber and rockets ahead of the Mustang, which isn’t revving its engine at all. Those are always ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "the best races",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/news/chevelle-races-nissan-skyline/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", when the guy you’re supposedly smoking doesn’t know there’s a race and isn’t pushing his car at all.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "For reasons we can only speculate about, the C7 Z06 suddenly veers left in front of the Mustang, spins out of the control, and goes over the island in the road. Not that it’s the main issue, but we’re 99-percent sure it’s gonna need quite the alignment and maybe some new suspension parts after that. Thankfully, the idiot didn’t get hit by oncoming traffic, but it looked kind of close with the first car to pass him by.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "We love powerful cars, but some people just aren’t cut out for them. For some, sticking to something like a Toyota Corolla might not be a bad thing.",
